&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate mastery of all Madison Reed systems, policies, processes and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and develop team members to ensure the highest level of team culture, guest satisfaction, and Hair Color Bar performance through aligning individuals’ unique talents and abilities with the most relevant responsibilities.&lt;/li&gt;
